Customer: Hello? Hello?
Executive: Ji, main IndiaMART se baat ho rahi hu, Gruhi mein.
Customer: Ha boliye.

Executive: Nahi sir, actually aapka ek feedback aaya hai. Feedback sir Rakhi ne diya hai ki aap satisfied nahi hai IndiaMART se, toh mujhe aap hi se baat karni hai.
Customer: Maine nahi diya hai, wo mera partner ne diya hai. Wo aap call kar lijiye, dusra number udhar hai. Toh usme call kar lijiye.
Executive: Theek hai, okay sir. Thank you.
Customer: Okay.
